@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> OnHold
OnHold --> Closed : review
Closed --> Pending : update
Closed : entry / log shipment
Pending --> Delivered : approve
Delivered --> Completed : update
Completed --> Archived : submit
Completed : entry / log shipment
Archived --> [*]
@enduml